# Default macro for /geant4-run.
# 1 GeV electron gun aimed along +z, fired into the example lead block.

# Threading commands (e.g. `/run/numberOfThreads 4`) belong here, BEFORE
# /run/initialize — Geant4 only honors them in the PreInit state. The
# shipped example main forces sequential mode, so adding threading here
# is a no-op until you switch G4RunManagerType::Serial to ::Default in
# the main and provide a thread-safe TTree filler.

/run/initialize

/gun/particle e-
/gun/energy 1 GeV
/gun/position 0 0 -200 mm
/gun/direction 0 0 1

/run/beamOn 1000
